// Real, date-anchored admissions calendar — the deterministic source for the
// Timeline. Dates live HERE in code (never generated by the AI, which would
// hallucinate or go stale) and are computed against "today" + the student's
// graduation year, so the same profile always yields the same plan.
//
// ⚠️ VERIFY ANNUALLY. SAT sittings and competition deadlines below are the
// curated 2026–27 cycle. They are presented in the UI as "confirm on the
// official site" with a register link — but the founder should re-check these
// against College Board / each competition each year and bump them. Sources are
// linked per item. Keeping them roughly right is far better than the old generic
// "register for the next SAT" with no date at all.

